name: Margaret River Deluxe Wine Tour
description:
Deluxe Wine Tour 

10am - 5pm daily  -  all ages and abilities.

Exclusive tour for 12 persons or less, individuals welcome.

Visit the best of Margaret River with our most qualified guide.

Gold Plate lunch at winery in Margaret River.

Coastal viewing of famous Margaret River surf, plus wine tasting.

For the dedicated wine enthusiast.

name: Bushtucker Winery & Brewery Tour - Ferguson Valley
description:
Ferguson Valley Winery & Brewery Tours depart daily 

10am - 5pm  - fun, informative, group and individual tours.

From Bunbury, Gelorup, Dallyalup, Australind, Eaton.

All ages and abilities welcome.

Visit 7 hill top wineries and breweries + cheese and galleries. 

Tastings of all wines, cheeses, gourmet produce included.

Brewery tastings at 2 breweries discounted for our guests.

Bring a happy smile for a brilliant fun day.

Call 08 9757 9084 to take advantage of HOT DEALS or CHECK ON OUR WEBSITE at www.bushtuckertours.com

name: Bushtucker River & Canoe Tour - Margaret River
description:
Bushtucker Cave & Canoe Tour daily on Margaret River 

9:45am - 2:00pm from Margaret River mouth, Prevelly.

2 - 5 seater canoes, all equipment provided, all ages and abilities.

Wild food lunch provided, special food requests - call 08 9757 9084.

Flat water canoeing, explore island, cliff, cave and river environment.

Bring a hat, open or closed shoes, bottle of water, camera.

Pick-up for guests with no transport, 9:30am 

Call 08 9757 9084 to take advantage of HOT DEALS or CHECK ON OUR WEBSITE at www.bushtuckertours.com

name: Bushtucker Winery & Brewery Tour - Margaret River
description:
Margaret River Winery & Brewery Tours depart daily 

10am - 5pm

From Busselton, Dunsborough, Margaret River and surrounds.

All ages and abilities welcome.

Visit 7 iconic Margaret River attractions.

Tastings of all wines, chocolate, cheeses, gourmet produce included.

A Brewery is visited on each tour.  There are 6 breweries in the Margaret River region.  Beer tastings are discounted on our tours.

Bring a happy smile for a brilliant fun day.

Call 08 9757 9084 to take advantage of HOT DEALS or CHECK ON OUR WEBSITE at www.bushtuckertours.com
